## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of up-to-date data and the inherent biases in sources. The complexity of illegal immigration means that motivations can vary widely among individuals, and not all factors may be captured in this report. Additionally, the reliance on secondary sources may not fully reflect the most current trends or policies affecting illegal immigration.